highlights.text: “עברתי רק כדי לראות” by Tomer Yosef and Ben Hendler is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 68 spots at #123.
“Hurricane” by Eden Golan is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #2.
Eden Hason has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “צוחקת ובוכה” is the highest at #7.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 314 weeks straight.
